<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hempen" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hempen,</orth> made of hemp: <cit><quote>h. tackle,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III Chor.</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III Chor.</bibl> <cit><quote>a h. caudle,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.7.95" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 7, 95</bibl></cit> (a halter). Metaphorically: <cit><quote>h. home-spuns,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 79</bibl></cit> (== of coarse manners).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>